data.description: JUST IN TIME FOR SUMMER. You will love this backyard oasis with a luxurious diving pool and spa as well as the outdoor living area and fire pit. The  expanded covered patio with vaulted cedar cover is a great space for entertaining and family living.The spacious backyard has lots of room to play. This exceptional Stone Hollow home on a quarter acre corner lot in Van Alstyne is conveniently located just under 2 minutes from US 75.  4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, 2 living, 2 dining, study and media room with a 3 CAR GARAGE. So many upgrades - including extra stone veneer, hand scraped hardwoods throughout the living areas and kitchen, stone fireplace, high end granite counters and painted cabinets and professional landscapping. The kitchen is a chef's dream with an abundance of storage and work spaces and kitchen island with breakfast bar. The open floor plan has a great flow for your family and for entertaining. The kids will love the space upstairs with game room and media.
